high_descs: Turn right to head down the passage and reach the bedroom on the right and reach the dresser.
Pick up the butterknife from the dresser.
Walk out the room and turn left to reach the kitchen and face the apple in the sink.
Cut the apple on the sink with the knife.
Head to the dining table on the right.
Put the butterknife on the diningtable.
Turn around and reach the apple.
Pick up a slice of apple from the sink.
Head left to reach the microwave.
Heat the apple slice in the microwave and take the apple slice out.
Turn around to reach the dining table.
Put the apple on the diningtable with the knife.
anns.task_desc: Put the heated slice of Apple on the DiningTable.

high_descs: Go straight until reaching the counters, then turn right and go into the hallway, entering the first door on the right and approaching the dresser just to the left.
Pick up the butter knife from the dresser.
Exit the room the way you came in, then turn left and go straight, then right into the kitchen area, stopping at the sink.
Slice the apple on the drainboard next to the sink.
Go right to the large white dining table.
Place the butter knife down on the table.
Return to the sliced apple.
Pick up one slice of the apple.
Go towards the microwave at the corner of the counters.
Use the microwave on the apple slice and pick it back up.
Go back to the dining table you put the knife down on.
Place the apple slice down on the table.
anns.task_desc: Place a microwaved apple slice on a dining table.

high_descs: Go toward the sink, turn right, go into the first door on the right and go to the dresser.
Pick up the butterknife from the dresser.
Exit the room, go left and then right into the kitchen to the apple in the sink.
Slice the apple on the sink.
Turn right and go to the diningtable.
Put the butterknife on the diningtable.
Turn right and go back to the apple in the sink.
Pick up a slice of apple from the sink.
Turn right and go to the microwave.
Put the apple slice in the microwave, turn the microwave on and then take out the apple slice.
Turn around and go back to the diningtable.
Place the apple slice on the diningtable near the knife.
anns.task_desc: Place an Apple slice on the DiningTable.
